
Adris n Mouloud Feraoun/Tasuqqilt

(...) M. G. d yiwen akken Ufransi n Dzayer 
ur tban ara akk ttajara-ines. 
Macci γef waya dγa i t-γucceγ,  
imi kan iγil tikta-ines ulac nnig-sent, 
zzelgent-as ula d tikli  
tikli d warraw-n tmurt-agi, (lizandijin) . 
Ad t-tafed ittmeslay-asen 
s ttnefxa d lqella n leqder,  
ama i wergaz ama i tmeṭṭut. 
Mara ittmeslay, 
izga issedda-d  tifyirin s taεrabt 
nebla ma yewwi-ten-id wawal. 
Armi d yiwen wass, kkreγ 
la s-ttmeslayeγ s yiwet akken n tegnawit, 
snulfaγ-tt-id nekkini, 
tettakanzi i teqbaylit. 
Rnu netta, nniγ-as, yakan,  
yif-it ma yuγal  
γer tutlayt n lejdud-ines ad as-iban rray
Tukkist seg "La Cité des Roses"Mouloud Feraoun
Asebter 95. Tizrigin Yamcom, 2007, Zzayer.
Yeffeγ-d udlis-a 25 n yiseggasen si tmettant-ines.
